{"tid":228162,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（無圖）王皓信係男神","createTime":"2017-05-03T16:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T16:34:48.000Z","uid":43641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37a81931c69736c3f75974072df224faed6cf15a","tid":228162,"uid":43641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:34:08.000Z","msg":"王皓信又型又高大唱歌又好聽做戲又好睇<br />\n之前致命復活有幕騎住電單車救個港女嗰幕型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又如羅家良二世 <br />\n唔明大台成日捧雪雪雪同洪永城嗰啲做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我敢講王皓信係大台最值得捧嘅男星係新一代男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c27dfbdd782fff69300b673748f566657fae147","tid":228162,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"Signal Wong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}